Using olive oil in a hair mask can do a lot for your hair. It can make it softer, keep it conditioned, and strengthen it. Below we have put together five different hair masks that incorporate olive oil. However, before we get into it, let‚Äôs look at how exactly olive oil helps your hair.
<h2>How Does Olive Oil Help Your Hair?</h2>
A hair mask made with olive oil can do wonders for hair that is dry, damaged, and brittle. Olive oil is a rich emollient that helps in conditioning hair, making it smooth and silky while improving its elasticity and tensile strength.¬† It also improves the quality of dull hair, making it look shiny and healthy. It even prevents breakage and adds shine.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id="hair_care_sidebar"][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:35:"How To Prepare Olive Oil Hair Masks";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:35:"how-to-prepare-olive-oil-hair-masks";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-04-20 11:51:13";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-04-20 11:51:13";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:41:"http://localhost/homemadesolutions/?p=643";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"644";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-04-14 12:43:51";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-04-14 12:43:51";s:12:"post_content";s:851:"[vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]Guava leaves have taken the internet by storm with claims of it being a miracle solution for hair loss. It is also gaining popularity as a hair thickening ingredient that promotes rapid hair growth. But how exactly are guava leaves beneficial for your hair?

